1. Create a ScreenGui in StarterGui , and rename it StatsGui.
2. Create 6 TextLabel to list all of the stats on the screen.
3. Rename them by their name ( example : energyLabel , healthLabel, .. ).
4. Create a LocalScript in the ScreenGui , and rename it StatsGuiUpdater.
5. Add the "StatsGuiUpdater.lua" code into it.
6. Create a "StatManager" script in ServerScriptService.
7. Add the "StatManager.lua" code into it.
